comment: Bass (LAL) sets the screen on Tucker (PHO) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Knight (PHO) splits his feet on the perimeter.
Chandler (PHO) is in the paint for longer than three seconds.
Nance Jr. (LAL) obtains a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact from Knight (PHO) as he contests the driving layup attempt.
Chandler (PHO) makes contact with Kelly (LAL), affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Nance Jr. (LAL) cleanly knocks the ball away from Booker (PHO).
Chandler (PHO) extends his arm and continues to move as he sets the screen on Williams (LAL) without giving him room to avoid the contact.
Kelly (LAL) and Tucker (PHO) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Teletovic (PHO) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Nance Jr. (LAL) that does not affect his shot attempt.
Tucker (PHO) dislodges Bass (LAL), affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Kelly (LAL) makes contact with the ball while part of it still remains in the cylinder above the basket ring.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court of Offensive Goaltending was upheld.
[Detectable with stop watch] Booker (PHO) is in the paint for longer than three seconds.
Booker (PHO) sets a legal screen on Bass (LAL) and falls to the ground after incidental contact.
Nance Jr. (LAL) sets the screen on Tucker (PHO) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Tucker (PHO) and Huertas (LAL) make incidental contact with one another while reaching for the loose ball.
[Observable in enhanced video] After Williams (LAL) gains possession of the loose ball, his foot touches the mid-court line.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the ball was last touched by Kelly (LAL) was upheld.
Williams (LAL) commits a take foul on Knight (PHO).
Williams (LAL) commits a take foul on Booker (PHO).
